<template>
    <v-network-graph
      class="graph"
      :node-list="nodeList"
      :edge-list="edgeList"
      
      
    />
  </template>
  
  <script>
  import { VNetworkGraph } from 'v-network-graph';
  
  export default {
    components: {
      VNetworkGraph
    },
    props: {
      nodeList: {
        type: Object,
        required: true
      },
      edgeList: {
        type: Object,
        required: true
      }
    },
    
  }
  </script>
  
  <style>
  .graph {
    width: 800px;
    height: 600px;
    border: 1px solid #000;
  }
  </style>
